         <div type="address"><address><addrLine><pb facs="1907_AS_RBH_1_00043"/><hi rend="pre-print">Dr. Arthur Schnitzler</hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="pre-print"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb168940">Wien XVIII. Spoettelgasse 7</rs>.</hi></addrLine></address><address><addrLine>Herrn <hi rend="latintype">Dr. Richard Beerhofmann</hi></addrLine><addrLine><rs ref="#pmb68" type="place">Wien XVIII</rs></addrLine><addrLine><rs type="place" ref="#pmb235251"><hi rend="latintype">Hasenauerstraße 59</hi></rs>.</addrLine></address></div>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><p><pb facs="1907_AS_RBH_1_00044"/>Wir bitten Sie und <rs type="person" ref="#pmb10860">Paula</rs> morgen <date>Din<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>tag</date><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><time>Abend</time> bei uns zu<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>pei<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>en. <rs type="person" ref="#pmb11485">Paul
                  Goldm.</rs> u <rs type="person" ref="#pmb26392">Leo Vanj.</rs><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ind ver<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>tändigt.
                  Ko<c rendition="#gemination-m">mm</c>en Sie nicht<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>pät. (<time>½ 8</time> etwa.)</p><closer>Herzlich<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t Ihr<lb/><signed>A.</signed></closer></div>
      </body>
